auto-crud
~~~~~~~~~

what
~~~~~~~~~
A simple PHP CRUD system.
As defined by wikipedia:
Create, read, update and delete (CRUD) are the four basic functions of persistent storage. 
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CRUD_(acronym)

why
~~~~~~~~~
Just because I needed a system like that, and didn't want to use a existing one.

how
~~~~~~~~~
It's all based on PHP and XML files for persist the configuration.

authors
